Introduction

Yoo Gwan Woo is a Taiwanese singer associated with Image Music. He previously belonged to the project boy group IXFORM. His solo debut came on November 13, 2023, with the digital single "The Man Who Was Caught in the Rain." He is well-known for his appearances on the survival shows Youth With You 3 and Starlight Boys.
